# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets redirect rules.
#
# Format:  <from>  <to>  <status>      — one rule per line, whitespace-separated.
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
#
# This file lives at the repo root because wrangler.jsonc sets assets.directory
# to "./". It is parsed by Workers and is NOT served as a public asset.
#
# IMPORTANT — redirects beat real files. Cloudflare: "Redirects are always
# followed, regardless of whether or not an asset matches the incoming request."
# So a bad rule can shadow a live page. Always redirect FROM a path you have
# actually removed, and never point a rule at itself.
#
# Limits: 2,000 static rules, 100 dynamic (wildcard/placeholder), 2,100 total,
# 1,000 characters per line.

